#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: ethio-cal.php
msgid "EthioCal – Ethiopian Calendar"
msgstr "ኢቲዮካል – የኢትዮጵያ ቀን መቁጠሪያ"

#. Description of the plugin
#: ethio-cal.php
msgid "A native Gutenberg block, shortcode, REST API, and developer API for the Ethiopian (Ge'ez) calendar."
msgstr "ለኢትዮጵያ (ግዕዝ) ቀን መቁጠሪያ ተወላጅ የጉተንበርግ ብሎክ፣ ሾርትኮድ፣ REST API እና ፈታሽ API።"

